The '''Republic Communications Tower''', located in [[Galactic City/Legends|Galactic City]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], was used as a communications station by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] during its last decades. It was presumably also used to assist the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

